<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Database Jemaat Terintegrasi - Sindika Platform</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        
        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse-glow {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 0.6; }
            50% { opacity: 1; }
        }
        
        @keyframes draw-line {
            from { stroke-dashoffset: 1000; }
            to { stroke-dashoffset: 0; }
        }
        
        .float-animation {
            animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        .connection-line {
            stroke-dasharray: 1000;
            stroke-dashoffset: 1000;
            animation: draw-line 2s ease-out forwards;
        }
        
        .node-glow {
            animation: pulse-glow 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        .feature-card {
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }
        
        @keyframes gradient-shift {
            0%, 100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
        }
        
        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1e40af, #7c3aed, #db2777, #1e40af);
            background-size: 200% auto;
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            animation: gradient-shift 6s ease infinite;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-800">
    <%- include('partials/_navbar') %>
    <div class="fixed top-0 left-0 w-full h-full overflow-hidden -z-10">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 -translate-x-1/3 w-[50rem] h-[50rem] bg-blue-200/40 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 translate-x-1/3 w-[50rem] h-[50rem] bg-purple-200/40 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[40rem] h-[40rem] bg-pink-200/30 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>
    
    <main class="w-full min-h-screen pt-32 pb-16 px-4">
        <section class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tight leading-tight">
                    Satu Sumber Kebenaran untuk <span class="gradient-text">Data Jemaat</span> Anda
                </h1>
                <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                    Ucapkan selamat tinggal pada data yang tersebar di spreadsheet, buku catatan, dan file yang berbeda. Sindika berfungsi sebagai "Buku Induk Digital" yang menyatukan semua informasi jemaat ke dalam satu platform yang aman, terstruktur, dan selalu valid.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Interactive Network Diagram -->
            <div class="my-20 w-full aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-white/80 to-white/40 backdrop-blur-2xl border border-white/50 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl p-12 relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50/50 to-purple-50/50"></div>
                
                <svg class="w-full h-full relative z-10" viewBox="0 0 800 450">
                    <!-- Connection Lines -->
                    <g class="opacity-40">
                        <!-- Sinode to Klasis connections -->
                        <line x1="400" y1="80" x2="200" y2="220" stroke="url(#gradient1)" stroke-width="3" class="connection-line" style="animation-delay: 0.3s"/>
                        <line x1="400" y1="80" x2="400" y2="220" stroke="url(#gradient1)" stroke-width="3" class="connection-line" style="animation-delay: 0.4s"/>
                        <line x1="400" y1="80" x2="600" y2="220" stroke="url(#gradient1)" stroke-width="3" class="connection-line" style="animation-delay: 0.5s"/>
                        
                        <!-- Klasis to Gereja connections -->
                        <line x1="200" y1="220" x2="100" y2="360" stroke="url(#gradient2)" stroke-width="2" class="connection-line" style="animation-delay: 0.8s"/>
                        <line x1="200" y1="220" x2="200" y2="360" stroke="url(#gradient2)" stroke-width="2" class="connection-line" style="animation-delay: 0.9s"/>
                        <line x1="200" y1="220" x2="300" y2="360" stroke="url(#gradient2)" stroke-width="2" class="connection-line" style="animation-delay: 1s"/>
                        
                        <line x1="400" y1="220" x2="400" y2="360" stroke="url(#gradient2)" stroke-width="2" class="connection-line" style="animation-delay: 1.1s"/>
                        <line x1="400" y1="220" x2="500" y2="360" stroke="url(#gradient2)" stroke-width="2" class="connection-line" style="animation-delay: 1.2s"/>
                        
                        <line x1="600" y1="220" x2="600" y2="360" stroke="url(#gradient2)" stroke-width="2" class="connection-line" style="animation-delay: 1.3s"/>
                        <line x1="600" y1="220" x2="700" y2="360" stroke="url(#gradient2)" stroke-width="2" class="connection-line" style="animation-delay: 1.4s"/>
                    </g>
                    
                    <!-- Gradients -->
                    <defs>
                        <linearGradient id="gradient1" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
                            <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#3b82f6;stop-opacity:1" />
                            <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#8b5cf6;stop-opacity:1" />
                        </linearGradient>
                        <linearGradient id="gradient2" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
                            <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#8b5cf6;stop-opacity:1" />
                            <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#ec4899;stop-opacity:1" />
                        </linearGradient>
                        <filter id="glow">
                            <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="4" result="coloredBlur"/>
                            <feMerge>
                                <feMergeNode in="coloredBlur"/>
                                <feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic"/>
                            </feMerge>
                        </filter>
                    </defs>
                    
                    <!-- Sinode Node -->
                    <g class="float-animation" style="animation-delay: 0s">
                        <circle cx="400" cy="80" r="45" fill="url(#gradient1)" class="node-glow" filter="url(#glow)"/>
                        <circle cx="400" cy="80" r="40" fill="white"/>
                        <text x="400" y="75" text-anchor="middle" class="text-xs font-bold fill-blue-700">SINODE</text>
                        <text x="400" y="90" text-anchor="middle" class="text-[10px] fill-slate-600">Pusat Data</text>
                    </g>
                    
                    <!-- Klasis Nodes -->
                    <g class="float-animation" style="animation-delay: 0.5s">
                        <circle cx="200" cy="220" r="35" fill="url(#gradient1)" class="node-glow" filter="url(#glow)"/>
                        <circle cx="200" cy="220" r="30" fill="white"/>
                        <text x="200" y="220" text-anchor="middle" class="text-[10px] font-bold fill-purple-700">KLASIS A</text>
                    </g>
                    
                    <g class="float-animation" style="animation-delay: 0.7s">
                        <circle cx="400" cy="220" r="35" fill="url(#gradient1)" class="node-glow" filter="url(#glow)"/>
                        <circle cx="400" cy="220" r="30" fill="white"/>
                        <text x="400" y="220" text-anchor="middle" class="text-[10px] font-bold fill-purple-700">KLASIS B</text>
                    </g>
                    
                    <g class="float-animation" style="animation-delay: 0.9s">
                        <circle cx="600" cy="220" r="35" fill="url(#gradient1)" class="node-glow" filter="url(#glow)"/>
                        <circle cx="600" cy="220" r="30" fill="white"/>
                        <text x="600" y="220" text-anchor="middle" class="text-[10px] font-bold fill-purple-700">KLASIS C</text>
                    </g>
                    
                    <!-- Gereja Nodes -->
                    <g class="float-animation" style="animation-delay: 1.1s">
                        <circle cx="100" cy="360" r="25" fill="url(#gradient2)" class="node-glow" filter="url(#glow)"/>
                        <circle cx="100" cy="360" r="22" fill="white"/>
                        <text x="100" y="363" text-anchor="middle" class="text-[9px] font-semibold fill-pink-700">Gereja 1</text>
                    </g>
                    
                    <g class="float-animation" style="animation-delay: 1.2s">
                        <circle cx="200" cy="360" r="25" fill="url(#gradient2)" class="node-glow" filter="url(#glow)"/>
                        <circle cx="200" cy="360" r="22" fill="white"/>
                        <text x="200" y="363" text-anchor="middle" class="text-[9px] font-semibold fill-pink-700">Gereja 2</text>
                    </g>
                    
                    <g class="float-animation" style="animation-delay: 1.3s">
                        <circle cx="300" cy="360" r="25" fill="url(#gradient2)" class="node-glow" filter="url(#glow)"/>
                        <circle cx="300" cy="360" r="22" fill="white"/>
                        <text x="300" y="363" text-anchor="middle" class="text-[9px] font-semibold fill-pink-700">Gereja 3</text>
                    </g>
                    
                    <g class="float-animation" style="animation-delay: 1.4s">
                        <circle cx="400" cy="360" r="25" fill="url(#gradient2)" class="node-glow" filter="url(#glow)"/>
                        <circle cx="400" cy="360" r="22" fill="white"/>
                        <text x="400" y="363" text-anchor="middle" class="text-[9px] font-semibold fill-pink-700">Gereja 4</text>
                    </g>
                    
                    <g class="float-animation" style="animation-delay: 1.5s">
                        <circle cx="500" cy="360" r="25" fill="url(#gradient2)" class="node-glow" filter="url(#glow)"/>
                        <circle cx="500" cy="360" r="22" fill="white"/>
                        <text x="500" y="363" text-anchor="middle" class="text-[9px] font-semibold fill-pink-700">Gereja 5</text>
                    </g>
                    
                    <g class="float-animation" style="animation-delay: 1.6s">
                        <circle cx="600" cy="360" r="25" fill="url(#gradient2)" class="node-glow" filter="url(#glow)"/>
                        <circle cx="600" cy="360" r="22" fill="white"/>
                        <text x="600" y="363" text-anchor="middle" class="text-[9px] font-semibold fill-pink-700">Gereja 6</text>
                    </g>
                    
                    <g class="float-animation" style="animation-delay: 1.7s">
                        <circle cx="700" cy="360" r="25" fill="url(#gradient2)" class="node-glow" filter="url(#glow)"/>
                        <circle cx="700" cy="360" r="22" fill="white"/>
                        <text x="700" y="363" text-anchor="middle" class="text-[9px] font-semibold fill-pink-700">Gereja 7</text>
                    </g>
                </svg>
                
                <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-center">
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm px-6 py-2 rounded-full shadow-lg">
                        ðŸ”— Integrasi Real-Time Sinode â†’ Klasis â†’ Gereja
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature Cards -->
            <div class="mt-20 grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="feature-card p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/90 to-white/60 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Profil Jemaat 360Â°</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Catat semua data demografis secara komprehensif, mulai dari informasi pribadi, status baptis, afiliasi rayon, hingga riwayat keterlibatan dalam pelayanan. Semua tersaji dalam satu tampilan profil yang mudah dibaca.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/90 to-white/60 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Struktur Keluarga Dinamis</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Petakan hubungan keluarga (suami, istri, anak) dengan mudah. Fitur ini membantu Anda memahami konteks keluarga setiap anggota untuk pelayanan yang lebih personal dan relevan.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/90 to-white/60 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-500 to-rose-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Pencarian & Segmentasi Canggih</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Butuh daftar semua pemuda di Rayon X atau semua jemaat yang belum mengikuti pembinaan? Gunakan fitur filter dan pencarian canggih untuk mendapatkan daftar yang Anda butuhkan dalam hitungan detik.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/90 to-white/60 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Sinkronisasi Real-Time</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Data yang diperbarui di tingkat gereja secara otomatis tersinkronisasi ke klasis dan sinode. Tidak ada lagi laporan manual atau data yang tidak konsisten antar tingkat organisasi.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/90 to-white/60 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Keamanan Berlapis</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Sistem hak akses berbasis peran memastikan setiap pengguna hanya dapat mengakses data yang relevan dengan tanggung jawab mereka. Enkripsi end-to-end melindungi privasi jemaat Anda.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/90 to-white/60 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-orange-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Laporan & Analitik Otomatis</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Dashboard interaktif memberikan insight real-time tentang pertumbuhan jemaat, demografi, dan tren pelayanan. Generate laporan komprehensif hanya dengan satu klik untuk keperluan rapat atau evaluasi.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

     <%- include('partials/_footer') %> 
</body>
</html>